{"tid":850560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北愛爾蘭兩周大嬰兒疑被強姦 25歲疑犯提堂","createTime":"2018-10-06T14:56:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T17:12:37.000Z","uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8019fbead33c09e25334aa287eb3f1cd5e9a44fd","tid":850560,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T14:56:32.000Z","msg":"北愛爾蘭一名兩周大嬰兒懷疑遭一名25歲男子強姦，目前正於兒童深切治療部留醫。疑犯被控強姦和意圖造成他人身體嚴重傷害罪，已於周二（2日）上庭。<br />\n<br />\n案中受害的嬰兒家住唐郡（County Down）一個村莊，現正於貝爾法斯特皇家兒童醫院（Royal Belfast Hospital for Sick Children）兒童深切治療部留醫。院方發言人表示，「由於家人要求保留私隱，我們不會進一步評論」。<br />\n<br />\n北愛爾蘭警方正調查本案。發言人表示，受害嬰兒身上「多處嚴重受傷」。警方已起訴一名25歲男子強姦和意圖造成他人身體嚴重傷害罪，疑犯已於周二（2日）上庭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181006/s00005/1538790229767\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181006%2Fs00005%2F1538790229767&d=zvjwJMnJdsybTlaoe9kqo7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=6767094c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181006%2Fs00005%2F1538790229767&h=5e470263\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181006/s00005/1538790229767</a><br />\n<br />\n鬼佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5734989fac98a13110e8cbb476774cb3434552c","tid":850560,"uid":20816,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T14:57:21.000Z","msg":"回教難民？"},{"pid":"b538823d25965ac1c0f923e113cdefffd094dfdb","tid":850560,"uid":72054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T14:57:51.000Z","msg":"兩周... 頭髮都未齊..."},{"pid":"4807d3992158906eefa656c9aa4479ea30b74ab8","tid":850560,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:07:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">快</span>"},{"pid":"481fb1227e63e29d7b9479f26733f68c82e7e449","tid":850560,"uid":60831,"l